    "created_at": "2016-04-22T21:08:26Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-04-22T21:08:26Z",
    "body": "We're really interested in working on this part of the Menu API for N1. The app's menus are growing, and some of the menus we want are used infrequently and are expensive to assemble. (See screenshot.) For our purposes, I think a single change would suffice: in place of an array of items, allow `submenu` to be a function which returns items, which is called when the submenu is about to be displayed.\n\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1037212/14754939/6df12124-0893-11e6-8d63-70fc4991774a.png)\n\nWould be interested to hear other specific use cases for menu delegates that folks have in mind. \n"
  },
