    "created_at": "2016-07-18T18:32:27Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-07-18T18:32:27Z",
    "body": "Facing this issue, I found this to work (or seem to):\n- `myMenu.clear()` to destroy all menu items,\n- `myMenu.append(new MenuItem({...}))` to add new items.\n\nIs it an acceptable by-pass?\n\nWhat worries me most is that the `clear()` function of [Menu API](https://github.com/electron/electron/blob/master/docs/api/menu.md) is not documented: maybe it is not recommended to call it...\n"
  },
